J4Wq57a0w">Quá Ngô giang - 過吳江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%AD/author-wTKRwNleDBqUp1bPjqhXCA">Vương Chí</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/T%C3%A2y-h%C3%A0-Kim-L%C4%83ng-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-Au8x0xwYW2LXafkG4bCq1w">Tây hà - Kim Lăng hoài cổ - 西河—金陵懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-aRbK_iKDMX5ibYXonb22rA">Chu Bang Ngạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thu%E1%BB%B5-h%E1%BA%A1c-ti%C3%AAn/poem-6_0Usxw1TWqKk_gkftte8A">Thuỵ hạc tiên - 瑞鶴仙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Thu%E1%BB%B7-trai/poem-Goycjtu5YUKUVNeSJZqivg">Thuỷ trai - 水齋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95-t%C3%ADch-k%E1%BB%B3-4-V%C4%A9nh-An-cung-Ti%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BB%A7-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-oJ3_lUOliYcBOCmvY_hK2A">Vịnh hoài cổ tích kỳ 4 - Vĩnh An cung, Tiên Chủ miếu - 詠懷古跡其四－永安宮，先主廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
